Package: httpproblems
Title: Report Errors in Web Applications with 'Problem Details' (RFC 7807)
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Aaron", family = "Jacobs", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "atheriel@gmail.com"))
Description: Tools for emitting the 'Problem Details' structure defined in
  'RFC' 7807 <https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7807> for reporting errors from
  'HTTP' servers in a standard way.
